  "question": "Which of the following characteristics is advantage of full thickness skin grafts over split thickness skin graft",
  "options": {
    "A": "Superior skin pigment match",
    "B": "Better resistance to infection",
    "C": "Large area of covarge",
    "D": "Less blood supply required",
    "E": "Lower incidence of contacture"
  },
