  "question": "In which of the following Shock is the neck veins distended",
  "options": {
    "A": "Septic shock early",
    "B": "Septic shock late",
    "C": "Traumatic shock",
    "D": "Hypovolemic shock",
    "E": "Cardiogenic Shock"
  },
